        <item>
            <title>中國 App Store 成人軟件登下載榜榜首，偽裝成學習 App + 無設定年齡限制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/09/apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/09/apple-app-store-porn-app-pretends-to-be-learning-app/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 09 Oct 2023 09:05:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198070</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>據中國媒體 IT 之家報道，Apple App Store 日前下架了一款登上免費榜首的「學習英文字母」 App，因為其本身原來竟是一款成人軟件。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/4702-9ebe97d2873ac20bddf4482f64330042-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/mobile/n/n/2023-10-08/doc-imzqhwff9971785.shtml">新浪</a></p><p>據 IT 之家報道，涉事軟件沒有年齡限制，分級屬 4 歲以上。IT 之家表示，該款成人軟件偽裝成英文字母學習軟件，但實際上會向用户提供賭博、色情網站的資訊和連結。IT 之家訪問了其中一名用家小同，其表示本身下載這款軟件是為了學習英文字母，但下載後發現這款軟件「掛羊頭賣狗肉」，實際上是一個提供色情資訊的軟件。小同認為這種以學習軟件為幌子的色情軟件很容易對小朋友造成不良影響，非常危險。IT 之家經已就事件向 Apple 查詢，Apple 方面回應指已經向 App 審核團隊反映。</p><p>IT 之家亦發現 Apple 免費榜首再出現偽裝成正經騎單車軟件的成人軟件，同樣亦不設年齡限制。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/1e93-fbea93344e7031bc61d63492166a6eb8-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198090" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-415x900.jpg 415w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-scaled.jpg 738w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/69ef-b68d394a29348291d1ef9b6207709d36-709x1536.jpg 709w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/mobile/n/n/2023-10-08/doc-imzqhwff9971785.shtml">新浪</a>、<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/723/418.htm">IT 之家</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
